{
  "texts": [
    "It enables a modular design of software microservices in bounded contexts defined by business domains.",
    "This design generates components of microservices that are loosely coupled and scalable [21].",
    "In the same spirit, data mesh decomposes data ownership and architecture into decentralized domain-oriented components.",
    "Defined domains become responsible for managing their own datasets and providing them to consumers.",
    "Data consumers may pull datasets from different domains."
  ]
}